dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Verso includes tourist advertisements: Budget rent a car; Pub old house: the coctail (sic) macer's and all kinds of drinks; Bartholomos travel agency; Hotel Cephalonia star; Mina tourism, travel & shipping agency. Ancillary maps shows location of Cephalania Island.
